<strong>NO operan por reembolso.</strong><br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br><b>*&nbsp;</b>&nbsp;Orientación veterinaria telefónica - las 24 horas los 365 dias del año&nbsp; &nbsp;<br><b>*&nbsp;</b>&nbsp;Desparacitación - hasta&nbsp;<strong>$500&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;<br><b>*&nbsp;</b>&nbsp;Pipeta antipulgas - hasta&nbsp;<strong>$500</strong>&nbsp;<br><b>*&nbsp;</b>&nbsp;Vacuna antirrábica - hasta&nbsp;<strong>$500&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;<br><b>*&nbsp;</b>&nbsp;Servicio de Cremación - hasta&nbsp;<strong>$1,500&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;<br><b>*&nbsp;</b>&nbsp;Servicio de esterilización - Pago directo,&nbsp;<strong>solo en red&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;<br><b>*&nbsp;</b>&nbsp;Baño y peluqueria canina - hasta&nbsp;<strong>$500&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;<br><b>*&nbsp;</b>&nbsp;Corte de uñas, limpieza de dientes y oidos (externo) - hasta&nbsp;<strong>$700</strong><br><b>*&nbsp;</b>&nbsp;Consulta veterinaria en red o domicilio - hasta&nbsp;<strong>$900</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;

